title: #2098 - Shane Gillis & Matt McCusker
description: Listen to this episode from The Joe Rogan Experience on Spotify. Shane Gillis and Matt McCuskerare stand-up comics and the hosts of "Matt and Shane's Secret Podcast." Catch Matt's comedy special "At the Speed of Light" on YouTube. Shane's latest special, "Beautiful Dogs," is on Netflix.  www.mattmccusker.com www.shanemgillis.com
